## Notes

- The Analytics component will automatically start collecting page view data when deployed to Vercel
- No configuration is required for basic analytics functionality
- The component is tree-shakeable and will not affect bundle size if analytics are disabled
- All pre-existing ESLint warnings in the codebase remain unchanged (no new warnings introduced)
